Punch and Zergling entered a room, spotting Teletran-1 and Teletran-
2.  Teletran-1 looking somewhat repaired.  Both Alliance members 
looked to each other, nodding.

Punch fired off a rocket at Teletran-1, Zergling firing off 20 rapid 
laser blasts at Teletran-1.
